{"tid":1507530,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"德魯納酒店結局","createTime":"2019-08-26T07:43:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T07:15:01.000Z","uid":143093,"like":2,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"080f6bb803165a4145987291b81a45a97a456093","tid":1507530,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:43:57.000Z","msg":"第15集：<br />\n具燦星呢集一定會咸能到扑街以為IU死咗，跟住佢一直留係酒店到做一直係到等IU返嚟，具燦星睇到IU啲野諗返起佢點相遇+點相愛etc<br />\n另一方面PO會同mina講佢會同佢阿妹一齊走，mina又咸到扑街<br />\n中間具燦星會同麻姑神/死神吹水，麻姑神會講埋啲好能玄好能中二病嘅野<br />\n呢集最尾具燦星做咗成年/幾年野會有幕係陰間見到個人影行出嚟<br />\n<br />\n16集：<br />\n個人影係IU嚟，因為陰間嘅時間同陽間唔同 所以要幾年時間<br />\n仲有麻姑神擺左朵花係具燦星個心口到，姐係話具燦星俾左生命IU，IU會同具燦星一齊老死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nPO走左之後，mina就成日去拜佢<br />\n完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母如果個結局唔係咁，我停出十日post<br />\n我都做到編劇啦 出一次sad ending啦dllm<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5a4a35d2ccecab643ac252969d2f3e5342fc9ea","tid":1507530,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:44:05.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣傳一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GJMrJb.jpg&h=cb7c9807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n901 和你塞  13:00 見   <a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY5bpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=41fe0086\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"a1c7b39f01ffb6c9c24f943a0d660d8635ad488b","tid":1507530,"uid":238483,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:44:55.000Z","msg":"樓主燈神"},{"pid":"0a64fba445e44758d16c497d86eeb4b95b8a644e","tid":1507530,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a1c7b39f01ffb6c9c24f943a0d660d8635ad488b","tid":1507530,"uid":238483,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-